It charges people to dump rubbish at the site during the day and the night, which it then sorts, treats and sends on for disposal elsewhere.

But residents say this practice does not happen and instead, over the past couple of 
years, Waste4Fuel has simply taken the money and let it stack up into a 
monstrous pile.

